author: rhuijben
msg: Fix basic tests 14 on Windows, by moving the check on whether an entry
must be removed directly, to mark_tree_deleted().
(mark_tree_deleted): If an entry is only scheduled for addition, just remove
the entry and make wc_db forget about its existance.

author: stylesen
msg: On the 1.6.x-r39692 branch, merge r39692 from trunk and resolve
Fix issue #3498 - Subversion password stores freeze Eclipse
and we are in interactive mode but have no unlock prompt function, don't
throw a "GNOME Keyring is locked and we are non-interactive" error;
instead, continue without unlocking it, so that the unlocking may be
handled by the default GNOME Keyring unlock dialog box.
